  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Grandson and grandmother drowned",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An eight-year-old child and the child's grandmother drowned while swimming in Meemure Pussefall in Udadumbara police area.",
        "Police say that the deceased child had come to Meemure area from Gamunupura Kudo Oya area with his father to visit his grandmother on the 12th and that evening while swimming in the waterfall with his grandmother, she saw the child drowning while trying to save him, the grandmother also drowned.",
        "The police say that the two deceased are A Ariavathy (59) and her grandson Tenuka Satsara Mihiranga (08).",
        "Further investigations are being conducted under the direction of the Chief Inspector of Police, Uda Dumbara Police Station."
      ],
